Newcastle Manager Pardew Charged for Media Comments, F.A. Says

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-09-01T09:58:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-01/newcastle-manager-pardew-charged-for-media-comments-f-a-says.html
Newcastle United manager  Alan Pardew 
was charged with improper conduct by  England ’s Football
Association for comments made prior to his club’s match against
rival Sunderland.  The F.A. didn’t disclose in a statement which comments
Pardew was cited for. Pardew has until Sept. 5 to respond, the
F.A. said. Newcastle won the game 1-0.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  